            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                    <h3 class="mb-0">How to Use the App</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5>Toggle the Daily Button</h5>
                    <p>On the home page, you'll see a large circular button with "I did it!" text. Click this button to mark today as complete. When clicked, the button will display a beautiful animated rainbow border to celebrate your accomplishment!</p>

                    <h5>View Your Progress</h5>
                    <p>Below the button, you'll find a calendar view showing your tracking history. Days when you completed your task are marked with green dots. You can navigate between months using the arrow buttons.</p>

                    <h5>Understanding the Calendar</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Green dots:</strong> Days when you successfully did the thing</li>
                        <li><strong>No dot:</strong> Days when you didn't complete your task</li>
                        <li><strong>Today:</strong> Highlighted with a blue border</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5>Data Storage</h5>
                    <p>Your progress is automatically saved in your browser's local storage. This means your data persists between sessions, but it's only available on the device and browser you're using.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                    <h3 class="mb-0">About</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="lead">This is a real-time tracking application to help ensure you do a daily thing each day.</p>
                    <p>Whether it's drinking enough water, taking a walk, practicing gratitude, or any other daily habit you want to build, "I Did a Thing!" helps you stay consistent and visualize your progress over time.</p>

                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        <h6 class="alert-heading">Pro Tips:</h6>
                        <ul class="mb-0">
                            <li>Set a specific daily goal to track</li>
                            <li>Check the app at the same time each day</li>
                            <li>Celebrate your streaks and don't be too hard on yourself for missed days</li>
                            <li>The app works offline once loaded, so you can track anywhere!</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Space for more info later -->
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h6>Coming Soon:</h6>
                        <p class="text-muted">Future updates may include streak counters, multiple habit tracking, and data export features.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
